{"tid":1216311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【商界】香港總商會遺憾示威演變暴力　懇請政府與大眾作有意義對話","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:45:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e47e511250c372dc9ee596e22ded8192c56d251","tid":1216311,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190613/s00001/1560413503544/【逃犯條例】總商會遺憾示威演變暴力-懇請政府與大眾作有意義對話\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F1560413503544%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%B8%BD%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%BC%94%E8%AE%8A%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E6%87%87%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%88%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%9C%BE%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=c9f34530\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F1560413503544%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E7%B8%BD%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%BC%94%E8%AE%8A%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E6%87%87%E8%AB%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%88%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%9C%BE%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1&h=bc9807cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190613/s00001/1560413503544/【逃犯條例】總商會遺憾示威演變暴力-懇請政府與大眾作有意義對話</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190613/s00001/1ec573f4f1be4497b62864dc70f6a81b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190613%2Fs00001%2F1ec573f4f1be4497b62864dc70f6a81b.jpg&h=445314df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港總商會（總商會）對昨日（12日）的示威行動演變為暴力事件深表遺憾。總商會主席夏雅朗表示：「我們完全尊重市民和平表達看法和意見的權利，但我們強烈譴責訴諸暴力的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n總商會表示認同草案背後的原則，然而，市民展開的大規模示威和抗議行動顯示，社會仍然深感憂慮。他續說：「我們懇請政府繼續聆聽持份者的聲音，並與社會大眾進行有意義的對話。」<br />\n<br />\n總商會總裁袁莎妮補充，商界關注事態發展。她表示：「我們促請各方保持克制，確保爭論不會影響企業對香港的信心，以及本港的國際聲譽。」"},{"pid":"c2ce56f54ecbdf853bbe34b97f502c1342292d4a","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"同自由相比，企業對香港信心同本港國際聲譽不值一提"},{"pid":"719702687d6d1b39067b3c8e0393a084004615de","tid":1216311,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2ce56f54ecbdf853bbe34b97f502c1342292d4a","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"同自由相比，企業對香港信心同本港國際聲譽不值一提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"人地啲大商家走曬，到時我地連飯都冇得食既時候你就唔方唔想自由了。"},{"pid":"4be71418670e9503ee6a372c44cd8e8cfa805e26","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"719702687d6d1b39067b3c8e0393a084004615de","tid":1216311,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2ce56f54ecbdf853bbe34b97f502c1342292d4a","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"同自由相比，企業對香港信心同本港國際聲譽不值一提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"人地啲大商家走曬，到時我地連飯都冇得食既時候你就唔方唔想自由了。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:35.000Z","msg":"過左逃犯條例唔走? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家冇人針對商家, 香港要繼續係自由城市先會有人敢投資"},{"pid":"a12967864d0b401225842968ae97f13d76b75fc5","tid":1216311,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4be71418670e9503ee6a372c44cd8e8cfa805e26","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"719702687d6d1b39067b3c8e0393a084004615de","tid":1216311,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c2ce56f54ecbdf853bbe34b97f502c1342292d4a","tid":1216311,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:51:45.000Z","msg":"同自由相比，企業對香港信心同本港國際聲譽不值一提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"人地啲大商家走曬，到時我地連飯都冇得食既時候你就唔方